## Initialization
# Playing around with commands

units lj
dimension 2
atom_style atomic
boundary p p p

## System Definition
# Rectangle with two circles 

region box block -25.5 25.5 -25.5 25.5 -5 5
create_box 2 box

region cyin cylinder z 0 0 20 0 1 side in
region cyou cylinder z 0 0 20 0 1 side out
create_atoms 1 random 500 123456 cyin
create_atoms 2 random 1000 123455 cyou

replicate 2 1 1

## Atom Information

pair_style lj/cut 2.5
pair_coeff 1 1 1.0 1.0
pair_coeff 2 2 0.5 3.0

mass 1 0.5
mass 2 0.5

#write_data initial.lammps

## Simulation settings
# minimization

thermo 10
minimize 0.0 1.0e-8 1000 100000

fix eq all nve
fix le all langevin 1.0 1.0 0.1 123
fix en all enforce2d
thermo 1000

dump dmp all atom 100 dump.eq.lammpstrj

timestep 1
run 5000
